Logo




Dear Customer,

We are writing to let you know that the authentication token associated  
with your DBS/POSB account is no longer valid. As a result, certain online  
banking services, including card-related transactions, may be temporarily  
affected.

To ensure uninterrupted access to your digital banking services, please  
complete the update of your DBS Digital Token.

Update Your DBS Digital Token

Important information:
After completing the update, please allow up to 12 hours before accessing  
your account. This processing period is required for the changes to take  
effect.


If you need assistance or further clarification, please contact the  
DBS/POSB customer service hotline.

Customers under DBS/POSB Treasures, Treasures Private Client, or Private  
Banking may reach out to the DBS/POSB Wealth Management hotline for  
dedicated support.

Thank you for your understanding and cooperation.

Yours sincerely,
DBS / POSB Customer Support Team



This is an automated notification. Please do not reply to this email.
Unsubscribe .




